M|references|**Posting frequency:** 3-5x per week
M|references|**Best times:** Tuesday-Thursday, 7-8am, 12pm, 5-6pm
M|references|**What works:**
M|references|- Personal stories with business lessons
M|references|- Contrarian takes on industry topics
